('840d76c8-50c6-44c6-8676-1a980178aeaf', 1, 'What is the calc() function used for?', 'mcq', '[{"text":"Performing calculations in CSS","is_correct":true},{"text":"Calling JavaScript","is_correct":false},{"text":"Counting elements","is_correct":false},{"text":"Computing colors","is_correct":false}]', 'Performing calculations in CSS', 1),
